title: Busta Rhymes and Voletta Wallace and Biggie's manager  Wayne Barrow
itunes:title: Busta Rhymes and Voletta Wallace and Biggie's manager  Wayne Barrow
description:
Today on the show we had a few guest with one we couldn't get physically but we were still able to get first timer on the show Busta Rhymes on Zoom. They spoke about his new album, the song he has with feature and who could challenge him in a versus battle, Also, we had a pleasure to have a mother of one of the greatest rappers alive Biggie Smalls! His mother Voletta Wallace and Biggies manager Wayne Barrow called in to speak about Biggie's legacy, Biggie being inducted in the Rock and Roll Hall of fame and more. Also, Charlamagne, gave Donkey of the Day to the White House spiritual advisor Paula White Cain for her election prayer.
